metadata.source: WHO Mental Health Atlas 2023, Global Burden of Disease Study 2023, IHME Global Health Data Exchange, World Bank Country Classifications
metadata.description: Comprehensive mental health treatment gaps analysis for all 194 WHO member states, based on latest available data
metadata.methodology: Data compiled from WHO Mental Health Atlas 2023, GBD 2023, World Bank income classifications, and peer-reviewed epidemiological studies. Treatment gaps calculated using WHO methodology.
metadata.confidenceLevel: 95% confidence intervals available. Data quality varies by country reporting capacity.
citations: WHO. (2023). Mental Health Atlas 2023. Geneva: World Health Organization.
GBD 2023 Mental Disorders Collaborators. (2024). Global, regional, and national burden of mental disorders. Lancet Psychiatry.
World Bank. (2024). World Bank Country and Lending Groups.
